<article
id="post-150224" class="post-150224 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail category-christianity category-featured category-terrorism category-war category-war-crimes"><h1>Why Obama is Right to avoid double standard about Modern Christian Atrocities</h1><div
class="meta clear"><div
class="author-meta">
<span
class="lion"></span>
By <a
href="http://www.juancole.com/author/jcedit" title="Posts by Juan Cole" rel="author">Juan Cole</a>
<span
class="div">|</span>
<a
title="Permalink to Why Obama is Right to avoid double standard about Modern Christian Atrocities" href="http://www.juancole.com/2015/02/standard-christian-atrocities.html" rel="bookmark">Feb. 7, 2015</a>
<span
class="div">|</span></div><div
class="icons-meta"><div
class="meta-without-print">
<span
class="meta-comments">
<a
href="#comments" title="Comment on 'Why Obama is Right to avoid double standard about Modern Christian Atrocities'"></a>
<span
class="meta-comments-number" >37</span>
</span><div
class='fv_sharing_round'>
<span
class="fvretweet "><a
class="image" target="_blank" onclick="pretty_social_increase_number('.fvretweet .twnumber');" href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.juancole.com%2F%3Fp%3D150224&amp;text=Why+Obama+is+Right+to+avoid+double+standard+about+Modern+Christian+Atrocities" title="Retweet 'Why Obama is Right to avoid double standard about Modern Christian Atrocities' on Twitter"><span>Retweet</span></a> <span
class="twnumber">148</span></span>
